    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Por Ambiente — Distribuição de Storage Accounts\n\nVisualização agrupada pela tag **ambiente** (ou **environment**). Ajuda a priorizar a análise: contas de desenvolvimento ou homologação são candidatas mais prováveis à remoção."
            },
            "name": "EnvironmentDescription"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| mv-expand connection = properties.privateLinkServiceConnections\r\n| extend targetResourceId = tolower(tostring(connection.properties.privateLinkServiceId))\r\n| where targetResourceId contains 'microsoft.storage/storageaccounts'\r\n| summarize PECount = count() by targetResourceId\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    resources\r\n    | where type =~ 'microsoft.storage/storageaccounts'\r\n    | extend _tagAmb = tostring(tags.ambiente)\r\n    | extend _tagAMB = tostring(tags.Ambiente)\r\n    | extend _tagenv = tostring(tags.environment)\r\n    | extend _tagENV = tostring(tags.Environment)\r\n    | extend Ambiente = case(\r\n        isnotempty(_tagAmb), _tagAmb,\r\n        isnotempty(_tagAMB), _tagAMB,\r\n        isnotempty(_tagenv), _tagenv,\r\n        isnotempty(_tagENV), _tagENV,\r\n        'Sem tag')\r\n    | project storageId = tolower(id), Ambiente\r\n) on $left.targetResourceId == $right.storageId\r\n| summarize StorageAccounts = dcount(targetResourceId), TotalPEs = sum(PECount) by Ambiente\r\n| order by StorageAccounts desc",
              "size": 1,
              "title": "Storage Accounts por Ambiente",
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "visualization": "piechart"
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "EnvironmentPie"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| mv-expand connection = properties.privateLinkServiceConnections\r\n| extend targetResourceId = tolower(tostring(connection.properties.privateLinkServiceId))\r\n| where targetResourceId contains 'microsoft.storage/storageaccounts'\r\n| extend subnetId = tostring(properties.subnet.id)\r\n| parse kind=regex subnetId with '/subscriptions/' peSubId '/resourceGroups/' peRG '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/' vnetName '/subnets/' subnetName\r\n| summarize PECount = count(), VNETs = dcount(vnetName) by targetResourceId\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    resources\r\n    | where type =~ 'microsoft.storage/storageaccounts'\r\n    | extend _tagAmb = tostring(tags.ambiente)\r\n    | extend _tagAMB = tostring(tags.Ambiente)\r\n    | extend _tagenv = tostring(tags.environment)\r\n    | extend _tagENV = tostring(tags.Environment)\r\n    | extend Ambiente = case(\r\n        isnotempty(_tagAmb), _tagAmb,\r\n        isnotempty(_tagAMB), _tagAMB,\r\n        isnotempty(_tagenv), _tagenv,\r\n        isnotempty(_tagENV), _tagENV,\r\n        'Sem tag')\r\n    | project storageId = tolower(id), Ambiente\r\n) on $left.targetResourceId == $right.storageId\r\n| summarize StorageAccounts = dcount(targetResourceId), TotalPEs = sum(PECount), VNETsDistintas = sum(VNETs) by Ambiente\r\n| order by StorageAccounts desc",
              "size": 0,
              "showAnalytics": true,
              "title": "Resumo por Ambiente",
              "exportFieldName": "Ambiente",
              "exportParameterName": "SelectedAmbiente",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "StorageAccounts",
                    "formatter": 4,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "blue"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "TotalPEs",
